<p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3月13日下午4点30分</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，经济管理学院辅导员队伍来到马场参与</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">学校植树活动。活动过程中，辅导员们个个热情高涨，分工合作，配合默契，挖坑、浇水、培土整个活动井然有序。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEJjVRicS41Wrk7xW3Gic9Jtv44KESUypPoUC8hFzMbpPbHaYoKxSrBFiaADHibDwcbBoLlt4fE8lHicBLQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="278" height="191" style="width: 278px; height: 191px;"/></span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; vertical-align: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">在这充满生机与希望的春天里，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; vertical-align: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">辅导员们用心种下了希望的树苗，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; vertical-align: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">愿小小的树苗向上生长，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; vertical-align: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">经历风雨的洗礼，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; vertical-align: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">长成参天大树。</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><p><section style="margin: 10px 5px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 4px 0px 0em; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(240, 250, 246);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 1em; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-left: 1px solid rgb(91, 189, 127); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(91, 189, 127); border-right: 1px solid rgb(91, 189, 127);"></section></section></section></p><p><br/></p>